
  Respecting users' privacy is a basic policy of WritingImproveHelper. We will not disclose, edit or disclose the user's registration information and the non-public content stored in the modified services, unless we consider it necessary to disclose such information in the following circumstances on the basis of good faith:

 (1) Comply with the relevant laws and regulations.
 
 (2) Follow the modified product service procedures.
 
 (3) Maintain the ownership of the modified trademark.
 
 (4) In case of emergency, we try our best to maintain the privacy and security of users and the public.
 
